{"parse":{"title":"Right2Water","pageid":44449911,"revid":832120886,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>\n<b>Right2Water</b> is a campaign to commit the <a href=\"/wiki/European_Union\" title=\"European Union\">European Union</a> and Member States to implement the human right to water and sanitation.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>It has three stated goals: \n</p>\n<ol><li>Guaranteed water and sanitation for all in Europe.</li>\n<li>No liberalisation of water services.</li>\n<li>Universal (Global) access to water and sanitation.</li></ol>\n<p>On the 21 March 2013, it became the first <a href=\"/wiki/European_Citizens%27_Initiative\" title=\"European Citizens&#39; Initiative\">European Citizens' Initiative</a> to collect more than a million signatures and they reached the minimum quota of signatures in seven countries on the 7 May 2013. It stopped the signature collection on the 7 September 2013, with a total of 1,857,605 signatures. The initiative was submitted to the <a href=\"/wiki/European_Commission\" title=\"European Commission\">European Commission</a> in December 2013 and the public hearing took place on the 17 February 2014 at the <a href=\"/wiki/European_Parliament\" title=\"European Parliament\">European Parliament</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> In March 2014, the Commission has adopted the Communication in response to the Right2Water initiative.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> On the 1 July 2015 the Roadmap for the evaluation of the Drinking Water Directive has been published by the European Commission.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In response, the European Parliament criticised the Commission for failing the meet the initiative's demands.<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> The report by <a href=\"/wiki/Sinn_F%C3%A9in\" title=\"Sinn F\u00e9in\">Sinn F\u00e9in</a> MEP <a href=\"/wiki/Lynn_Boylan\" title=\"Lynn Boylan\">Lynn Boylan</a> called on the Commission \"to recognise that affordable access to water is a basic human right.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Right2Water&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/European_Citizens%27_Initiative\" title=\"European Citizens&#39; Initiative\">European Citizens' Initiative</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Right2Water&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.right2water.eu/node/37/view\">\"About our Campaign | Water campaign\"</a>. <i>www.right2water.eu</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-03-01</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=www.right2water.eu&amp;rft.atitle=About+our+Campaign+%7C+Water+campaign&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.right2water.eu%2Fnode%2F37%2Fview&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARight2Water\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/en/news-room/content/20140204STO34708/html/Right-to-water-attend\">http://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/en/news-room/content/20140204STO34708/html/Right-to-water-attend</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Communication from the Commission on the European Citizens' Initiative \"Water and sanitation are a human right! Water is a public good, not a commodity!\" <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://ec.europa.eu/transparency/regdoc/rep/1/2014/EN/1-2014-177-EN-F1-1.Pdf\">http://ec.europa.eu/transparency/regdoc/rep/1/2014/EN/1-2014-177-EN-F1-1.Pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://ec.europa.eu/smart-regulation/roadmaps/docs/2015_env_041_drinking_water_en.pdf\">http://ec.europa.eu/smart-regulation/roadmaps/docs/2015_env_041_drinking_water_en.pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/en/news-room/20150903IPR91525/right2water-citizens%E2%80%99-initiative-commission-must-act-say-meps\">\"Right2water citizens' initiative: Commission must act, say MEPs | News | European Parliament\"</a>. <i>News | European Parliament</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-03-01</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=News+%7C+European+Parliament&amp;rft.atitle=Right2water+citizens%E2%80%99+initiative%3A+Commission+must+act%2C+say+MEPs+%7C+News+%7C+European+Parliament&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.europarl.europa.eu%2Fnews%2Fen%2Fnews-room%2F20150903IPR91525%2Fright2water-citizens%25E2%2580%2599-initiative-commission-must-act-say-meps&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARight2Water\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/en/news-room/20150903IPR91525/right2water-citizens%E2%80%99-initiative-commission-must-act-say-meps\">\"Right2water citizens' initiative: Commission must act, say MEPs | News | European Parliament\"</a>. <i>News | European Parliament</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-03-01</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=News+%7C+European+Parliament&amp;rft.atitle=Right2water+citizens%E2%80%99+initiative%3A+Commission+must+act%2C+say+MEPs+%7C+News+%7C+European+Parliament&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.europarl.europa.eu%2Fnews%2Fen%2Fnews-room%2F20150903IPR91525%2Fright2water-citizens%25E2%2580%2599-initiative-commission-must-act-say-meps&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARight2Water\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1270\nCached time: 20180910105414\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.100 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.126 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 28